title: Prana Health Cafe
description: A small quaint vegetarian cafe in Rajajinagar, Bangalore, offering pure vegetarian and vegan food. Serves a variety of food ranging from soups, salads, sandwiches, burgers, rolls & wraps to nutritious milkshakes, smoothies and other beverages. Does not use artificial preservatives, additives or coloring agents; also avoids sugar, so most of the dishes are jaggery based. Specializes in millet based food. Also serves fruit sorbets.
streetAddress: 600, 1st Main Road, Dr Rajkumar Road, 2nd block, Rajaji Nagar, Bangalore
